.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH build 1  "build " 
.SH NAME
build \- Build a .docx from a Lexicon Markdown file
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbuild\fR [\fB\-o\fR|\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-s\fR|\fB\-\-style\fR] [\fB\-\-signatures\fR] [\fB\-\-pdf\-renderer\fR] [\fB\-\-strict\fR] [\fB\-\-font\-family\fR] [\fB\-\-font\-size\fR] [\fB\-\-heading\-font\-family\fR] [\fB\-\-title\-size\fR] [\fB\-\-heading1\-size\fR] [\fB\-\-heading2\-size\fR] [\fB\-\-heading\-space\-before\fR] [\fB\-\-heading\-space\-after\fR] [\fB\-\-paragraph\-space\-before\fR] [\fB\-\-paragraph\-space\-after\fR] [\fB\-\-line\-spacing\fR] [\fB\-\-defined\-term\-style\fR] [\fB\-\-brand\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-page\-size\fR] [\fB\-\-margin\-top\fR] [\fB\-\-margin\-bottom\fR] [\fB\-\-margin\-left\fR] [\fB\-\-margin\-right\fR] [\fB\-\-indent\-per\-level\fR] [\fB\-\-hanging\-indent\fR] [\fB\-\-body\-align\-first\-level\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-body\-align\-first\-level\fR] [\fB\-\-recitals\-align\-first\-level\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-recitals\-align\-first\-level\fR] [\fB\-\-date\-format\fR] [\fB\-\-cover\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-cover\fR] [\fB\-\-cover\-between\-label\fR] [\fB\-\-cover\-party\-format\fR] [\fB\-\-cover\-ref\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-cover\-ref\fR] [\fB\-\-cover\-author\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-cover\-author\fR] [\fB\-\-cover\-status\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-cover\-status\fR] [\fB\-\-toc\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-toc\fR] [\fB\-\-toc\-heading\fR] [\fB\-\-footer\-ref\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-footer\-ref\fR] [\fB\-\-footer\-page\-number\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-footer\-page\-number\fR] [\fB\-\-footer\-version\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-footer\-version\fR] [\fB\-\-preamble\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-preamble\fR] [\fB\-\-preamble\-style\fR] [\fB\-\-schedule\-position\fR] [\fB\-\-schedule\-order\fR] [\fB\-\-enable\-signatures\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-signatures\fR] [\fB\-\-signatures\-heading\fR] [\fB\-\-signatures\-template\fR] [\fB\-\-signatures\-separate\-pages\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIINPUT\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Build a .docx from a Lexicon Markdown file
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-o\fR, \fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR
Output .docx file (defaults to input stem + .docx)
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-style\fR \fI<STYLE>\fR
Style configuration file (TOML). If not specified, searches for style.toml in the input file\*(Aqs directory, then in $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/lexicon/
.TP
\fB\-\-signatures\fR \fI<SIGNATURES>\fR
Signature definitions file (TOML). If not specified, searches for signatures.toml in the input file\*(Aqs directory, then in $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/lexicon/
.TP
\fB\-\-pdf\-renderer\fR \fI<PDF_RENDERER>\fR [default: auto]
PDF rendering backend for exhibit imports
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRauto, pdftoppm]
.TP
\fB\-\-strict\fR
Fail on warnings (exit code 1)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIINPUT\fR>
Input Lexicon Markdown file
.SH TYPOGRAPHY
.TP
\fB\-\-font\-family\fR \fI<FONT_FAMILY>\fR
Body text font family
.TP
\fB\-\-font\-size\fR \fI<FONT_SIZE>\fR
Body text font size in points
.TP
\fB\-\-heading\-font\-family\fR \fI<HEADING_FONT_FAMILY>\fR
Heading font family
.TP
\fB\-\-title\-size\fR \fI<TITLE_SIZE>\fR
Document title font size in points
.TP
\fB\-\-heading1\-size\fR \fI<HEADING1_SIZE>\fR
Level 1 heading size in points
.TP
\fB\-\-heading2\-size\fR \fI<HEADING2_SIZE>\fR
Level 2 heading size in points
.TP
\fB\-\-heading\-space\-before\fR \fI<HEADING_SPACE_BEFORE>\fR
Space before section headings in points
.TP
\fB\-\-heading\-space\-after\fR \fI<HEADING_SPACE_AFTER>\fR
Space after section headings in points
.TP
\fB\-\-paragraph\-space\-before\fR \fI<PARAGRAPH_SPACE_BEFORE>\fR
Space before paragraphs in points
.TP
\fB\-\-paragraph\-space\-after\fR \fI<PARAGRAPH_SPACE_AFTER>\fR
Space after paragraphs in points
.TP
\fB\-\-line\-spacing\fR \fI<LINE_SPACING>\fR
Line spacing multiplier
.TP
\fB\-\-defined\-term\-style\fR \fI<DEFINED_TERM_STYLE>\fR
Defined term style
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRbold, quoted, bold\-quoted]
.TP
\fB\-\-brand\-color\fR \fI<BRAND_COLOR>\fR
Brand color as hex (e.g. "#2E5090" or "2E5090")
.SH "PAGE LAYOUT"
.TP
\fB\-\-page\-size\fR \fI<PAGE_SIZE>\fR
Page size
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRa4, letter]
.TP
\fB\-\-margin\-top\fR \fI<MARGIN_TOP>\fR
Top margin in cm
.TP
\fB\-\-margin\-bottom\fR \fI<MARGIN_BOTTOM>\fR
Bottom margin in cm
.TP
\fB\-\-margin\-left\fR \fI<MARGIN_LEFT>\fR
Left margin in cm
.TP
\fB\-\-margin\-right\fR \fI<MARGIN_RIGHT>\fR
Right margin in cm
.SH "CLAUSE INDENTATION"
.TP
\fB\-\-indent\-per\-level\fR \fI<INDENT_PER_LEVEL>\fR
Indent per clause level in cm
.TP
\fB\-\-hanging\-indent\fR \fI<HANGING_INDENT>\fR
Hanging indent for clause numbers in cm
.TP
\fB\-\-body\-align\-first\-level\fR
Align first\-level body clauses with second level
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-body\-align\-first\-level\fR
Do not align first\-level body clauses with second level
.TP
\fB\-\-recitals\-align\-first\-level\fR
Align first\-level recital clauses with second level
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-recitals\-align\-first\-level\fR
Do not align first\-level recital clauses with second level
.SH FORMATTING
.TP
\fB\-\-date\-format\fR \fI<DATE_FORMAT>\fR
Date format string (chrono strftime syntax)
.SH "COVER PAGE"
.TP
\fB\-\-cover\fR
Enable cover page
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-cover\fR
Disable cover page
.TP
\fB\-\-cover\-between\-label\fR \fI<COVER_BETWEEN_LABEL>\fR
Cover page "between" label
.TP
\fB\-\-cover\-party\-format\fR \fI<COVER_PARTY_FORMAT>\fR
Cover page party format
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRname\-spec\-role, name\-role, name\-only]
.TP
\fB\-\-cover\-ref\fR
Show reference on cover page
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-cover\-ref\fR
Hide reference on cover page
.TP
\fB\-\-cover\-author\fR
Show author on cover page
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-cover\-author\fR
Hide author on cover page
.TP
\fB\-\-cover\-status\fR
Show status on cover page
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-cover\-status\fR
Hide status on cover page
.SH "TABLE OF CONTENTS"
.TP
\fB\-\-toc\fR
Enable table of contents
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-toc\fR
Disable table of contents
.TP
\fB\-\-toc\-heading\fR \fI<TOC_HEADING>\fR
Table of contents heading text
.SH FOOTER
.TP
\fB\-\-footer\-ref\fR
Show reference in footer
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-footer\-ref\fR
Hide reference in footer
.TP
\fB\-\-footer\-page\-number\fR
Show page numbers in footer
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-footer\-page\-number\fR
Hide page numbers in footer
.TP
\fB\-\-footer\-version\fR
Show version in footer (appended to reference)
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-footer\-version\fR
Hide version in footer
.SH PREAMBLE
.TP
\fB\-\-preamble\fR
Enable parties preamble
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-preamble\fR
Disable parties preamble
.TP
\fB\-\-preamble\-style\fR \fI<PREAMBLE_STYLE>\fR
Preamble style
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRsimple, prose, custom]
.SH SCHEDULE
.TP
\fB\-\-schedule\-position\fR \fI<SCHEDULE_POSITION>\fR
Schedule position in the document
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRend, after\-toc]
.TP
\fB\-\-schedule\-order\fR \fI<SCHEDULE_ORDER>\fR
Schedule item ordering
.br

.br
[\fIpossible values: \fRdocument, alphabetical]
.SH SIGNATURES
.TP
\fB\-\-enable\-signatures\fR
Enable signature pages
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-signatures\fR
Disable signature pages
.TP
\fB\-\-signatures\-heading\fR \fI<SIGNATURES_HEADING>\fR
Signature pages heading text
.TP
\fB\-\-signatures\-template\fR \fI<SIGNATURES_TEMPLATE>\fR
Default signature template key
.TP
\fB\-\-signatures\-separate\-pages\fR
Each signature block on its own page
